                  indexspecs(Specs).

          indexspec(Spec) :-
                  Spec=..[_F|Args],
                  list(Args,argspec).

     *Usage:* `indexspecs(IndexSpecs)'
        - _Description:_ `IndexSpecs' is an index specification.


