     variables are unified accordingly inside the template:
          ?- file_to_string('template.html',_S),
             html_template(_S,Terms,[content=b("hello world!"),bgcolor="white"]).

          Terms = [env(html,[],["
          ",env(body,[bgcolor="white"],["
          ",b("hello world!"),"
          "]),"
          "]),"
          "] ?

